resources.name: Real Time Reporting API : Real Time Data

queryParameters.name: ids
queryParameters.description: Unique table ID for retrieving Analytics data. Table ID is of the form ga:XXXX, where XXXX is the Analytics view (profile) ID.

queryParameters.name: metrics
queryParameters.description: A comma-separated list of Analytics metrics. E.g., 'rt:activeUsers'. At least one metric must be specified.

queryParameters.name: dimensions
queryParameters.description: A comma-separated list of real-time dimensions. E.g., 'rt:medium,rt:city'.

queryParameters.name: filters
queryParameters.description: A comma-separated list of dimension or metric filters to be applied to real-time data.

queryParameters.name: max-results
queryParameters.description: The maximum number of entries to include in this feed.

queryParameters.name: sort
queryParameters.description: A comma-separated list of dimensions or metrics that determine the sort order for real-time data.
